{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Cap airport drop-off and pick-up fees at \u00a35 across UK airports",
        "additional_details": "UK airports have increased drop-off and pick-up charges in recent years. What started at around \u00a35 for a few minutes has risen sharply, with some airports now charging up to \u00a310, such as Gatwick Airport. Passengers already pay Air Passenger Duty and other travel costs, yet must pay extra simply to drop off or collect someone. These fees also affect minicabs, black cabs and ride-hailing services, forcing higher fares. The Government should cap these charges at \u00a35 and prevent further increases.",
        "background": "Introduce legislation to cap airport drop-off and pick-up charges at \u00a35 across all UK airports and prevent any further increases. The Government should regulate these charges to ensure they remain fair and reasonable for passengers, drivers and transport providers.",
        "closed_at": null,
